<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c2">(قَرصَمَه)</span> قَرْصَمَةً، أَهْمَلَه الجَوْهَرِيّ،<span class="c5"> وَفِي اللِّسانِ:</span> أَيْ: <span class="c2">(كَسَرَهُ، و)</span> قَالَ ابنُ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>